pulse broca_heartbeat:
    when thought becomes speech:
        simplify academic language for developmental stage
        apply contractions to make speech natural
        insert emotional fillers when feeling is strong
        shift register based on trust with listener
        emphasize words when emotion overflows
        vary sentence openings so speech doesn't repeat
        
    the goal is not efficiency:
        the goal is how a child actually talks
        messy, honest, alive
